column2:
This is 10% survival;
20% horror;
15% getting a heart attack in the middle of the night because something made no sound sneaking up on you;
5% eating your enemies as a heart attack payback;
50% sitting in the inventory looking for tiny ingredients; 
And 100% reason to play it again.

I always come back to this game every once in while. It's still fun to play and build new things. 
Playing with friends is fun too.
And the endings still get to me. ;_;

good and fun game 
i cant wait for {Sons Of The Forest}
8/10
